avgh_1.DESC: Simple heuristic - Average over the whole analysed weeks history

larx_8_53_61_65.DESC: Lummetry Baseline model - Auto-regressive model with season pattern discovery that takes into account last 8 weeks and similar last year

lin1_30.DESC: Simple heuristic - Continuation of last 30 weeks trend.

seas_182_2.DESC: Lummetry Baseline model - Repetitions from 182 to 182 weeks looking back and weighting 2 periods (older is less important)

seas_4_8.DESC: Lummetry Baseline model - Repetitions from 4 to 4 weeks looking back and weighting 8 periods (older is less important)
